== Introduction ==

[[Image:Movie_Workbench_icon.svg|24px]] [[Movie_Workbench|Movie]] is an [https://www.freecad.org/addons.php external workbench] to animate cameras and objects, and to record and play videos.

== Toolbars ==

=== Cameras and objects tools ===

* [[Image:Movie_CreateMovieCamera.svg|24px]] [[Movie_CreateMovieCamera|MovieCamera]]

* [[Image:Movie_EnableMovieCamera.svg|24px]] [[Movie_EnableMovieCamera|Enable a MovieCamera]]

* [[Image:Movie_SetMoviePosA.svg|24px]] [[Movie_SetMoviePosA|Set position A]]

* [[Image:Movie_SetMoviePosB.svg|24px]] [[Movie_SetMoviePosB|Set position B]]

* [[Image:Movie_CreateMovieObjects.svg|24px]] [[Movie_CreateMovieObjects|MovieObjects]]

* [[Image:Movie_EnableMovieObjects.svg|24px]] [[Movie_EnableMovieObjects|Enable a MovieObjects]]

* [[Image:Movie_SetMovieObjectsAxis.svg|24px]] [[Movie_SetMovieObjectsAxis|Set an axis]]

* [[Image:Movie_ExcludeMovieObjects.svg|24px]] [[Movie_ExcludeMovieObjects|Exclude a MovieObjects]]

=== Animation tools ===

* [[Image:Movie_IniMovieAnimation.svg|24px]] [[Movie_IniMovieAnimation|Return to beginning]]

* [[Image:Movie_PrevMovieAnimation.svg|24px]] [[Movie_PrevMovieAnimation|Take a step back]]

* [[Image:Movie_PlayBackwardMovieAnimation.svg|24px]] [[Movie_PlayBackwardMovieAnimation|Play backward the animation]]

* [[Image:Movie_PauseMovieAnimation.svg|24px]] [[Movie_PauseMovieAnimation|Pause the animation]]

* [[Image:Movie_PlayMovieAnimation.svg|24px]] [[Movie_PlayMovieAnimation|Play the animation]]

* [[Image:Movie_PostMovieAnimation.svg|24px]] [[Movie_PostMovieAnimation|Move one step forward]]

* [[Image:Movie_EndMovieAnimation.svg|24px]] [[Movie_EndMovieAnimation|Move to the end]]

=== Record and play tools ===

* [[Image:Movie_CreateClapperboard.svg|24px]] [[Movie_CreateClapperboard|Clapperboard]]

* [[Image:Movie_EnableMovieClapperboard.svg|24px]] [[Movie_EnableMovieClapperboard|Enables a Clapperboard]]

* [[Image:Movie_StartRecord3DView.svg|24px]] [[Movie_StartRecord3DView|"R1" - Record 3DViews]]

* [[Image:Movie_StartRecordRender.svg|24px]] [[Movie_StartRecordRender|"R2" - Record Renders]]

* [[Image:Movie_StopRecordCamera.svg|24px]] [[Movie_StopRecordCamera|Stop Recording]]

* [[Image:Movie_CreateVideo.svg|24px]] [[Movie_CreateVideo|Create video]]

* [[Image:Movie_PlayVideo.svg|24px]] [[Movie_PlayVideo|Play video]]

== Installation ==

The [[Movie_Workbench|Movie Workbench]] is available through the [[Std_AddonMgr|Addon Manager]]. Any Movie 3rd party dependencies should be managed automatically through the Addon Manager. 

